Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.13,0:01:25.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"沙滩小镇或铩羽而归-威廉·杜威传"\N{\rENG}"Beach City or bust: The tale of William Dewey."\N
