Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他内心的,挣扎?\N{\rENG}See his struggles?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伟大的威廉·杜威从不,犹豫!\N{\rENG}The great William Dewey didn't struggle.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他做任何事都是一次成功-\N{\rENG}He was good at everything on the first try --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像我写的剧本\N{\rENG}just like me when I wrote this play.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不用改任何一个字\N{\rENG}Not a single word needs to be changed.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但,也许-\N{\rENG}But maybe --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要忘了是谁出的钱\N{\rENG}Don't forget who's funding this.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么,彩排的不错,先生们\N{\rENG}Well, nice hustle, gentlemen.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.03,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}坚持下去\N{\rENG}Keep it up.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.03,0:03:38.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}遵命\N{\rENG}Aye, aye.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这会是场灾难\N{\rENG}This is gonna be a disaster.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.42,0:03:42.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是个非常辣鸡的故事\N{\rENG}It's a terrible story.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}威廉·杜威太假了\N{\rENG}William Dewey is totally unbelievable.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为他能变到15米高?\N{\rENG}'Cause he grows 50 feet?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,他没有个性\N{\rENG}No, he's got no character.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但剧本一直在说他有多好啊\N{\rENG}But the script kept saying he was really good.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}正是如此\N{\rENG}Exactly.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人怎么可能没有缺陷?\N{\rENG}How can a guy have no faults?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人必须有缺陷\N{\rENG}To be human is to be flawed.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真正的英雄一定有内心斗争\N{\rENG}A real hero must struggle.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}说的,太好了!\N{\rENG}That's so beautiful.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且,完全没有体现在\N{\rENG}And, also, totally not represented\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杜威市长的剧本中\N{\rENG}in mayor Dewey's script.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的第一部戏-很可能也是最后一部\N{\rENG}My first play -- and probably my last.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿,珍珠\N{\rENG}Hey, Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠?\N{\rENG}Pearl?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文,你回来啦\N{\rENG}Steven, you're back.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.47,0:04:21.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊\N{\rENG}Yeah.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}演艺圈真是不好混啊\N{\rENG}Show business is rough.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有什么我可以帮忙的吗?\N{\rENG}Is there something I can help you with?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}除非你能让威廉·杜威变得有趣\N{\rENG}Not unless you can make William Dewey interesting.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你怎么知道的威廉·杜威?\N{\rENG}How do you know William Dewey?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要在这部戏中出演他\N{\rENG}I'm gonna be him in this play.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但他非常无趣\N{\rENG}But he's totally boring.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他很完美,而且从不犯错\N{\rENG}He's perfect, and he never makes mistakes.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真希望我也能这么评价自己啊\N{\rENG}Wish I could say the same for myself.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊,但没人是那样\N{\rENG}Yeah, but nobody's like that.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}每个人都可能出错,\N{\rENG}Everybody gets stuff wrong.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}之后再不断努力--这并不容易\N{\rENG}And then you have to keep going, and it's hard,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而这也是为什么坚持如此重要\N{\rENG}which is why it's great when you never stop trying.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你什么时候变得这么睿智了?\N{\rENG}When did you get so smart?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯...这不只是无聊\N{\rENG}Hmm. This isn't just boring.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且非常失实\N{\rENG}It's historically inaccurate.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁写的?\N{\rENG}Who wrote this?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杜威市长\N{\rENG}Mayor Dewey.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他当时又不在那里\N{\rENG}He wasn't even there.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我在\N{\rENG}But I was.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.10,0:05:02.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你当时在场?\N{\rENG}You were there?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么,到底发生了什么?\N{\rENG}Wait, what really happened?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}首先,\N{\rENG}Well, for starters,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\"硬朗般英俊"听起来太客气了\N{\rENG}"ruggedly handsome" seems rather generous.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文...\N{\rENG}Steven...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这太真实了!\N{\rENG}This is so real.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这看起来像是亲身经历过的人写的!\N{\rENG}It's like it was written by someone who lived it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就是这样!\N{\rENG}It was.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道你能否看出来,\N{\rENG}And I don't know if you can tell,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但,段子是我写的!\N{\rENG}but I wrote the jokes.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我当然看得出来\N{\rENG}I can tell.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真是太勇敢,太热烈,太...\N{\rENG}It's so gritty, so passionate, so...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尊重史实?\N{\rENG}Historically accurate?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有反转?\N{\rENG}And the drama?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这才是我们该演的剧本\N{\rENG}This is the play we should be doing.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那开始吧\N{\rENG}Let's do it then.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咱们演这个版本吧\N{\rENG}Let's put on this version of the play.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但该怎么办?\N{\rENG}But how?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们需要新的服装,新的道具-\N{\rENG}We'd need new costumes, new props --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.05,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们没有时间了\N{\rENG}we have no time.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且杜威市长会搞死我们的\N{\rENG}And mayor Dewey will have our heads.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但杰米,你自己说过-\N{\rENG}But Jamie, you said it yourself --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真正的英雄会有内心斗争\N{\rENG}"a real hero struggles."\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天哪,你说的没错!\N{\rENG}Ah, jiminy, you're right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这部戏明天晚上表演时\N{\rENG}This show will go on tomorrow night\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}由你出演威廉·杜威\N{\rENG}with you as captain William Dewey\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我则表演剩下的角色\N{\rENG}and I as the remaining roles.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}剩下的所有吗?\N{\rENG}All of them?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所有!\N{\rENG}All of them.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.87,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Sh...boom, ahh,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.08,0:06:01.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}表演\N{\rENG}acting.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能,做你旁边吗?\N{\rENG}Mind if I have a seat?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可-以吧\N{\rENG}Okay...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,你造吗,我写的剧本呦\N{\rENG}Oh, you know, I wrote this play.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我希望杜威市长不要对改动太过生气\N{\rENG}I hope mayor Dewey isn't mad about the changes\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}走一步看一步吧\N{\rENG}guess we'll have to see.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你紧张吗?\N{\rENG}Are you nervous?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然\N{\rENG}Of course.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这对我的生涯至关重要\N{\rENG}This could either make or break my career.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可能失去邮局的工作?\N{\rENG}You could lose your job at the post office?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这事关我的个人爱好啊\N{\rENG}This could either make or break my hobby.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}演戏\N{\rENG}Acting.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}木板先生和木板小姐们,\N{\rENG}Boardies and gentleboardies,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今晚,我非常高兴能像你们奉上...\N{\rENG}tonight, I am thrilled to present to you...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}威廉·杜威传\N{\rENG}"The tale of William Dewey."\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}耶!沙滩镇最叼!\N{\rENG}Yeah -- Beach City rules.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘～\N{\rENG}Shh.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,船长啊,我的船长,\N{\rENG}Oh, captain, my captain,\N
Dialogue: 600,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.90,Hint,,0,0,0,,“O Captain! My Captain!”致敬沃尔特·惠特曼的同名诗歌与“死亡诗社”
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有多久我们远航舰船的柔软舰首\N{\rENG}how long until the soft lips of our sailing ship\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}亲上新大陆那粗糙的胡茬?\N{\rENG}kiss the rugged beard of new lands?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.09,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道我们已经航行了好几个月了,\N{\rENG}I know we've been journeying for many months,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但肯定我们会遇到什么的\N{\rENG}but surely we'll run into something soon.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大海肯定没那么宽广吧?\N{\rENG}The ocean can't be that big.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他在那,嗨,史蒂文\N{\rENG}There he is. Hi, Steven.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是如此的有才啊\N{\rENG}You're so talented.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在我的老家我被称作"蠢蛋杜威"\N{\rENG}Back home they called me "Dewey the dunce,"\N
Dialogue: 600,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.20,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处可猜测威廉·杜威是以哥伦布为原型的——二者都来自于欧洲，都被家乡人蔑视，\N都发现了有原住民的大陆（水晶战士）
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人们说我发现不了陆地,即使我就站在上面\N{\rENG}said I couldn't find land even if I was standing on it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}搞毛...\N{\rENG}What the...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在我开始害怕他们说的是对的\N{\rENG}And I'm starting to fear that they were right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那在船左侧突然出现的光是什么?\N{\rENG}What light through yon stage left breaks?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,又发生了什么?\N{\rENG}Oh, what now?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是东面,而且我们是水晶战士\N{\rENG}It is the east, and we are The Crystal Gems.\N
Dialogue: 600,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.58,Hint,,0,0,0,,此处台词致敬莎士比亚的“罗密欧与朱丽叶”的原句——\N"But soft! What light through yonder window breaks? It is the east, and Juliet is the sun"
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.79,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}蛤?这不在剧本中啊\N{\rENG}What? This wasn't in the script.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这也不包含在预算中\N{\rENG}This wasn't in the budget, either.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}你好,我是珍珠\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}Greetings. I am Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.96,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}而且我来\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}And I come to you\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.66,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}是以信使的身份代表伟大的,\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}as a messenger of the brilliant,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.38,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}罗丝·石英!\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}Rose Quartz.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.12,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}我们要求你掉转船头\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}We ask that you turn your ship around.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.72,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}你们前往的土地\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}The land you are headed for\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.97,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}对于你们人类太过危险\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}is no walk in the park for your species.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}胡扯\N{\rENG}Nonsense.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我才不会听你们这种人的话\N{\rENG}I won't take orders from the likes of you.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.88,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HDDF699&}好吧,那么...\N{\rENG}{\c&HDDF699&}Well, then...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.85,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H811CC0&}你必须回头,否则就会被跳船\N{\rENG}{\c&H811CC0&}You should turn around lest you fall into the sea.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.12,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H811CC0&}你也知道,\N{\rENG}{\c&H811CC0&}And you know,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.90,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&H811CC0&}人类不怎么会游泳\N{\rENG}{\c&H811CC0&}humans aren't very good swimmers.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.08,Normal Dialog Text,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}{\c&HD897C1&}他们不会\N{\rENG}{\c&HD897C1&}They ain't.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来我只能回家了\N{\rENG}I'll just return home\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如同一个失败的蠢蛋\N{\rENG}like the failure dunce I am.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,我甚至都不能搞定船帆\N{\rENG}Ugh. I can't even turn a sail right.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么我总是遭受挫折?\N{\rENG}Why must I always struggle?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,老爸,那真是个屌丝\N{\rENG}Wow, dad, what a loser.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.62,0:08:10.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,船长,我的船长\N{\rENG}Oh, captain, my captain,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们已经从路线漂流出了好几英里了\N{\rENG}we've drifted Miles from our course.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这些波涛我之前可没见过\N{\rENG}These waves are nothing like I've ever seen before.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}胡扯!这只是毛毛雨而已\N{\rENG}Nonsense. This is only a drizzle.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,也许是场夏天的雷阵雨\N{\rENG}Okay, maybe a light summer storm.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}左舷那边是什么?\N{\rENG}What's that portside?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.02,0:08:26.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}操作杆\N{\rENG}Lever.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢\N{\rENG}Oh.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}船长,它抓住我了\N{\rENG}Captain, it's got me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴迪大副!\N{\rENG}First mate buddy.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不论如何,千万不要放弃你的搜寻\N{\rENG}Whatever you do, don't give up your search.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.96,0:08:41.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是我认识的最勇敢的人,因为你坚持尝试,\N{\rENG}You're the bravest man I know, because you try,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}即使你已经失败了无数次\N{\rENG}even though you fail so, so much.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴迪,不～!\N{\rENG}Buddy, noooo!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.62,0:08:53.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,巴迪,你死的好冤啊～\N{\rENG}Oh, buddy, a stale biscuit to the end.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而现在我的船将沉入深渊\N{\rENG}And now my boat will sink into the depths.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}多灾多难的蠢蛋杜威\N{\rENG}Dewey the disastrous dunce.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.94,0:09:02.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是什么?\N{\rENG}What's this?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的凤尾鱼啊!四重掐头掌!\N{\rENG}Holy anchovies. The quadruple noogie.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.23,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个只存在于传说中的招式\N{\rENG}A move that's only been spoken of in legends.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!它朝这里来了!\N{\rENG}Ah. It heads this way.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,求求你,掐头神,不要伤害我\N{\rENG}Oh, please, goddess of noogies, don't hurt me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔,我成功了!\N{\rENG}Whoa. I've made it!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}陆地!甜美的,坚实的陆地!\N{\rENG}Land! Sweet, solid land!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你,女巨人\N{\rENG}Thank you, giant woman.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你也许不想要呆在这里,这块土地非常危险\N{\rENG}You may not want to stay, this land is dangerous.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,我会留下\N{\rENG}No, I will stay.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为我是威廉·杜威,\N{\rENG}For I am William Dewey,\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我并不会因失败而放弃\N{\rENG}and I don't give up in the face of failure.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而这也让我变得如此伟大\N{\rENG}That's what makes me great.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Very well then.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我不保证我不会再次插手的\N{\rENG}But I can't promise you I won't interfere again.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我应该用这块新陆地的名字\N{\rENG}I shall name this new land\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}纪念我死去的大副,巴迪\N{\rENG}in honor of my dead first mate, buddy.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.34,0:09:49.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还活着!\N{\rENG}I'm alive.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,就叫沙滩市吧\N{\rENG}Okay, Beach City it is.\N
Dialogue: 500,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.34,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs96\bord0\shad0\frz348.7\pos(680,244)}{\c&H6341E2&}选{\c&HF36450&}杜{\c&H6341E2&}威
Dialogue: 500,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.34,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs96\bord0\shad0\frz18.68\pos(1100,230)}{\c&H6341E2&}当{\c&HF36450&}市{\c&H6341E2&}长
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What?\N
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很高兴知道曾祖父是个有缺陷的活生生的人物\N{\rENG}Nice to know great grandpa was a real person with flaws.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}很大胆啊,老爸\N{\rENG}Gutsy move dad.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杜威市长!\N{\rENG}Mayor Dewey!\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}市长-\N{\rENG}Mayor --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.45,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个给你,这个给你...\N{\rENG}one for you, and one for you...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打扰一下\N{\rENG}Excuse me.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.99,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我能跟天才交谈一下吗\N{\rENG}If I could have a moment with the talent.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.22,0:10:14.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦～哦\N{\rENG}Oh.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}杰米-\N{\rENG}Jamie.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,耶!\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做的太棒了\N{\rENG}Fantastic work.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我喜欢那条信息-"请投给杜威市长"\N{\rENG}I loved the message. "Vote mayor Dewey."\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}要不我再给你安排个位置-\N{\rENG}How about I offer you another role --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}沙滩市社区剧院的首席导演\N{\rENG}lead director of Beach City community theater.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能制作更多的戏剧-\N{\rENG}You could put on more plays --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只要预算允许的话\N{\rENG}as long as the budget allows it.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,谢谢,先生\N{\rENG}Uh, thank you, sir.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}许多功劳属于珍珠\N{\rENG}A lot of the credit should go to Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可以说她是"内部情报源"\N{\rENG}You could say she was an "inside source."\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是个多才多艺的宝石人\N{\rENG}I am a gem of many talents --\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}专注事实是我的能力之一\N{\rENG}a dedication to fact is just one of them.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你保存了我的家族传奇\N{\rENG}Thank you for preserving my legacy.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}朋友间200年算什么?\N{\rENG}Oh, what's 200 years between friends.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么...\N{\rENG}Well...\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我得走了\N{\rENG}I must be off then\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得去享受选民们的称赞了\N{\rENG}to bask in the adulation of my constituents.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道吗,我不记得有个竞选标语\N{\rENG}You know, I don't remember there being a campaign slogan\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在故事的结尾\N{\rENG}at the end of that story.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}艺术并不总是遵循逻辑的,珍珠\N{\rENG}Art doesn't always need a reason, Pearl.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有的时候只在于让观众高兴\N{\rENG}Sometimes it's just gotta make the audience happy.\N
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.35,0:11:09.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是为什么总要以段子结尾\N{\rENG}That's why you always end on a joke.\N
